name: Maduro Corona
additionalNotes:
The Davidoff Corona Maduro features a Nicaraguan sun-grown maduro wrapper surrounding four interior leaves, all of Dominican origin. The size is unique for a “corona,” at just 4 1/2 inches long but 46 ring gauge, a short but stout shape sometimes referred to as a Corona Extra.
